channel.title: Oraculum - By Pot up pls && Asshole_Rule. <3
channel.description:
[img]http://i54.tinypic.com/b8p6wg.jpg[/img]
[u][b]Introduction. [/b][/u] So basically, i have been very bored lately, so i thought, why not make a RSPS? So i'm here now, Developing one, Along side Asshole_rule, WE Have Both Came to a Decision On a server name, the server is going to be named "Oraculum" We both Also liked the name "Incipere" So Asshole_rule, Flipped a coin lol. this server is going to be based on economy and good skilling! Where you make your money from skilling, Such as herblore - Making your own super pots. I am using the base Of Project insanity, with none off that 543538958 loading 42094 shit.
[b]-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------[/b]
[u][b]Unique.[/b][/u] I want this server, to be Really unique, but im going too need your guys help, With suggestions and what not. I will be changing the home, but i do not know where Yet. Nick is going to Develop A new "master" skill cape, which is beast, it is going to be like this; http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SHbm-Z-ykGU& (that is nick, on his previous server.)
[u][b]Money.[/b][/u] I have money, to buy the vps, domains And advertisements So we will not need to worry about that, so the server should be 24-7 without lagg.
[b]-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------[/b]
[b][u]Server Goals.[/u][/b] - [b]Very[/b] Stable Server. - Unique Features. - New Home. (Keldagrim) - Npc/Player Clipping. - Very good Economy. - A Great player base, during the week/Weekends. [b]-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------[/b]
[u][b]Update Log.[/b][/u] [code] - Fixed logout exception. - Farming skill done. - Herblore skill done. - Got a slow start on npc clipping, but it's still a start. - Cooking skill done. - worked stability. [/code] Credits to Josh for the banner.
WE'RE IN NEED A GOOD SERVER BANNER, IF YOU'RE GOOD AT GFX, PLEASE LET ME KNOW. <3
Added Farming, Still a few bugs too be fixed. Asshole_rule. <3 Video Of farming. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xqKJMf_itaw
Herblore. http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K4Bft-Csg0A
Cooking. http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7hQISZzIf2k
Pictures coming soon.
